{"tid":1484154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人遊行無朋友好慘","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:47:20.000Z","uid":203508,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"57af1661c4c12359834467ecd767e08a8b3d8edf","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"地區的毒撚需要愛<br />\n平時隠青毒撚已經受盡白眼 心理折磨<br />\n出嚟遊行更加需要大家俾啲關心 俾啲自信<br />\n一個人行全日除左叫口號就無同過人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到個個巴絲一一group group齊上齊落真心覺得個公民社會無我份<br />\n大家叫到一個人行既 可唔可以主動俾啲溫暖佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsiC1dK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsiC1dK.png&h=ce154707&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"622873c49e8165fde9abe2e92cccbf6576f6a551","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"90c9afc6bd0d19a40de8f01392c8959ddecac288","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761d5ab2020764dbdda376e1892e8f59cc27b977","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔係香港人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dc7d59a4249757422b781f8ea4c0e108339295","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e85d2bc6ce1625ba48cb0d8e57036b973295a8d","tid":1484154,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"一出到黎個個都係兄弟姊妹巴打絲打啦，不過我都明，一個人出去發夢/示威係真係好撚悶，你下次試下做帶頭嗌一次口號，之後同人爹兩句，應該會肯傾計嘅。<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借推，大學生（急需有去過exchange 嘅學生）請幫個忙填問卷籌錢比612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8vzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=cf960e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6</a><br />\n<br />\n原post：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430200</a>"},{"pid":"2323331664d325fd2bb4daff528face740367e29","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd08fad68e25889b815321454d65fced4334bab3","tid":1484154,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"一個人出黎<br />\n有時有心情咪出一兩句聲<br />\n有人應咪傾計<br />\n戴住口罩 會有多啲自信"},{"pid":"8b88249c6231239aaebf6725cd1642ffa0a63b23","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"8e510ff1e4e647c2c5766646ca94f6686a61f0b9","tid":1484154,"uid":208417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"761d5ab2020764dbdda376e1892e8f59cc27b977","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔係香港人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"我都係自己行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9ff3d553c6b3a546c65a4dff0391e509c4c9c9","tid":1484154,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e510ff1e4e647c2c5766646ca94f6686a61f0b9","tid":1484154,"uid":208417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"